                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Un Don Juan, fier sous sa blouse,\nLui dit : « Viens au bois un moment,\nPuis je jure que je t’épouse ! »\nMais Rose sait très bien qu’il ment."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "On murmure que le vicaire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Cherche à prêcher aux Trois-Ormeaux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Rose ne s’effarouche guère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Et rit très fort de ses grands mots.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "On murmure que le vicaire\nCherche à prêcher aux Trois-Ormeaux.\nRose ne s’effarouche guère\nEt rit très fort de ses grands mots."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Rose va, narguant tout le monde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Très sage, on ne peut le nier.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "C’est le temps de la neige blonde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Il pleut des fleurs de marronnier !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Rose va, narguant tout le monde,\nTrès sage, on ne peut le nier.\nC’est le temps de la neige blonde,\nIl pleut des fleurs de marronnier !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Rose va, le chemin rayonne",
