                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Tout sourit. Et Rose, mignonne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Donne un sourire aux vieilles gens.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Rose va, le chemin rayonne\nDe soleil, de parfums, de chants.\nTout sourit. Et Rose, mignonne,\nDonne un sourire aux vieilles gens."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Que deviendra — t-elle ? Sans doute,",
